{"tid":90172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國湖北山崩壓垮飯店 15人遭活埋 已知2死3傷","createTime":"2017-01-21T22:36:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T08:15:09.000Z","uid":52651,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1076923049a02e06cc417eed2e0495398b7df155","tid":90172,"uid":52651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T22:36:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1954812\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1954812&d=wzPql2HN1U%2FdtEo8BWkm%2BXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=5e05affb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1954812&h=0a8f7618\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1954812</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國湖北一處飯店遭山崩壓垮，15人遭到掩埋，目前研判12人遇難，3人獲救。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，湖北南樟縣一處飯店20日晚間突然發生山崩，將飯店部分房屋壓垮，事發後大批搜救人員進駐搶救，經初步核定，事發時受困的飯店內人員共15人，搜救人員陸續救出5人，但其中2人傷重不治。"},{"pid":"1f68c5d0fb9573381ac9e1ef7b3928cbeb75112c","tid":90172,"uid":4105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T22:37:56.000Z","msg":"小鳳姐"},{"pid":"2b6478d27590e0fd380a5d84eabcbfd8d25350ba","tid":90172,"uid":60113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T23:07:42.000Z","msg":"sor禁錯負皮"},{"pid":"c82779da9ed35be53c3e69d54a5c69002c6343c3","tid":90172,"uid":58247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T23:50:45.000Z","msg":"好囉好囉 過唔到年"},{"pid":"d653a25bd2266e83655e04717d416b8de173714b","tid":90172,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T23:51:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"010fe784056d3c1c6db07059b736d0e97ba59322","tid":90172,"uid":1672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T23:53:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/075306_ec1c578fa2f3d63a692655f3d694d45b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https